title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (11): Structured Prediction w/ Local Dependence
description:
This lecture (by Xuezhe Ma) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Why Local Independence Assumptions?
* Conditional Random Fields
* Considering Reward in Training

Sorry, there was a mishap with recording the slides, but you can find them below:
Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-11-crf.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/e5sPNlgbZAE
Next Video: https://youtu.be/7rp2c7JVymE

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
